# Intermediate-Algorithm-Scripting
Answer of intermediate Algorithm Scripting in freeCodeCamp

Add all numbers.

Hints
- Use rest operator to converse a numbers into an array

-Use forEach 

- or Use reduce

//use reduce
function addallNumbers(...numbers){
    return numbers.reduce((acc, curr) => acc+curr); 
    
}
console.log(addallNumbers(1,2,4,5));

//Use forEach

function addallNumbes(...numbers){
let total=0;
return numbers.forEach(num => tatal += num );
}
console.log(addallNumbers(1,2,4,5));
